Routes

Method

Route

Description

GET

/analyticsapi/static

Get all static records

GET

/analyticsapi/static/id

Get the static record with the given id

POST

/analyticsapi/static

Create a new static record with a random id

PUT

/analyticsapi/static/id

Replace the static record with the given id, or create it if the record does not exist

DELETE

/analyticsapi/static/id

Delete the static record with the given id

Method

Route

Description

GET

/analyticsapi/activity

Get all activity records

GET

/analyticsapi/activity/id

Get the activity record with the given id

POST

/analyticsapi/activity

Create a new activity record with a random id

POST

/analyticsapi/activity/id

Append to the existing activity record for the given id (used instead of PUT if using sendBeacon)

PUT

/analyticsapi/activity/id

Replace the activity record with the given id, or create it if the record does not exist

PATCH

/analyticsapi/activity/id

Append to the existing activity record for the given id 

DELETE

/analyticsapi/activity/id

Delete the activity record with the given id
